K06acip-k_lha_sa-034-001:122b-21: de bzhin du chos kyi rnam grangs 'di ni /
K06acip-k_lha_sa-034-001:122b-24: mi cang shes rnams kyis bklag pa dang /
K06acip-k_lha_sa-034-001:122b-26: rab tu bstan pa'i nye bar spyod pa dang /
K06acip-k_lha_sa-034-001:122b-29: de dag gi bkod pa chen po dang /
K06acip-k_lha_sa-034-001:122b-31: chos kyi snang ba chen po byed par 'gyur /
K06acip-k_lha_sa-034-001:123a-0: de dag chos kyi rnam grangs 'di la @123a *//
K06acip-k_lha_sa-034-001:123a-1: chos kyi dga' ba chen po myong bar 'gyur ro //
K06acip-k_lha_sa-034-001:123a-2: gang chos kyi rnam grangs 'di las tshul gcig tsam 'dzin pa de dag kyang mchog tu dga' ba dang ldan par 'gyur na; gang thams cad rdzogs par bris pa dang /
K06acip-k_lha_sa-034-001:123a-6: rgyas par byed pa lta ci smos /
K06acip-k_lha_sa-034-001:123a-7: chos kyi rnam grangs 'dis mi'i dbang po dang /
K06acip-k_lha_sa-034-001:123a-8: mi cang shes de dag bzung bar 'gyur ro //
K06acip-k_lha_sa-034-001:123a-10: cang shes ma yin pa rnams kyi spyod yul ma yin no //
K06acip-k_lha_sa-034-001:123a-11: rab kyi rtsal gyis rnam par gnon pa /
K06acip-k_lha_sa-034-001:123a-13: the tshom thams cad gcod pa'i phyir ngas de dag smras so //
K06acip-k_lha_sa-034-001:123a-14: chos kyi rnam grangs 'di bshad pa na byang chub sems dpa' du ma dpag tu med pa dag gis mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa thob par gyur to //
K06acip-k_lha_sa-034-001:123a-15: sems can grangs med dpag tu med pa dag gis bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu sems bskyed de /
K06acip-k_lha_sa-034-001:123a-16: de dag byang chub tu nges par 'gyur bar de bzhin gshegs pas bstan to //
K06acip-k_lha_sa-034-001:123a-17: bcom ldan 'das kyis de skad ces bka' stsal nas byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po rab kyi rtsal gyis rnam par gnon pa dang /
K06acip-k_lha_sa-034-001:123b-0: lto 'phye chen po dang bcas pa'i 'jig rten yid rangs te bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa la mngon par @123b bstod do //
K06acip-k_lha_sa-034-001:123b-1: phan yon gyi le'u zhes bya ste /
K06acip-k_lha_sa-034-001:123b-3: 'phags pa rab kyi rtsal gyis rnam par gnon pas zhus pa shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa bstan pa rdzogs so ////
K06acip-k_lha_sa-034-001:123b-4: rgya gar gyi mkhan po sh'i lendra bo dhi dang /
K06acip-k_lha_sa-034-001:123b-6: zhu chen gyi lo tstsha ba bandhe ye shes sdes bsgyur cid zhus te /
K06acip-k_lha_sa-034-001:123b-7: skad gsar bcad kyis kyang bcos nas gtan la phab pa'o //
